snippet.title: Dinoblade Steam Wishlist Game Trailer
snippet.description:
Dinoblade is now available to Steam Wishlist! Started out as just animations for my demo reel, to gaining so much attention to make a game out of it so here we are. Dinoblade has been in development for a little over 1 year now so it is still in early stages but wishlisting this will help alot! Thank you!
Wishlist here:
https://store.steampowered.com/app/3440070/Dinoblade/

Music by Jacob Lizotte
